show.title: Don't Get Your Heart Fluttering for Me
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/Ete5TY
show.description: Pinky, a young woman bound by an ancient pact and possessing mysterious powers, descends into the modern world to find her destined husband, Rocky. But Rocky is now a cold, powerful CEO, completely unaware of their connection. When Pinky suddenly appears, claiming to be his wife based on a childhood marriage contract, Rocky dismisses her as delusional. However, dark forces plague Rocky's family, particularly his ailing grandfather, who seems afflicted by a sinister spell orchestrated by greedy relatives. As Pinky uses her unique abilities to intervene, the lines between myth and reality blur. Faced with a world of magic he doesn't understand and a family he can't trust, will Rocky accept the impossible woman who claims his heart, or will darker schemes prevail?
